The Revenue Operations Analytics template creates datasets based on your Salesforce configuration.
Dataset Name	Contents	Special Requirements
Account	Data about accounts.	None
Opportunity	Data about opportunities. Includes records joined on opportunity split and opportunity amount.	None
Opportunity Splits	Data about opportunities splits. The cumulative split amount is used for the opportunity amount.	Included only if opportunity splits is enabled
Forecast<Data about forecasts, including the item, quota, and type.	Included only if forecasting is enabled
User Roles	Data about users, including role, opportunity, and role hierarchy.	Included only if user roles is enabled
Forecasting Quota	Data about forecasting quotas.	None
Product	Data about your products.	None
Oppty Products	Data about product opportunities.	None
title: Revenue Operations Analytics
